race.comment: GOT A CARD (1) is better than last start when sixth (19.25) in a Grade 5 at this track over 320m. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Looks the one to beat on his best form. QUARTIC FUNCTION (7) missed the frame and safely held latest finishing 6th at Dubbo following on from a win (18.43) at this track the start prior. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and four minor placings to her credit. Key runner who gets her chance to atone. ROAR OF THUNDER (8) scored (23.30) last time out at this track in a Grade 5 and will break from box 8 for the first time. Is yet to taste defeat at this distance. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Bold showing expected again. CHATTAHOOCHE (2) cannot be left out over a shorter journey.
